eu.bavenir.ogwapi.commons.messages

Class CodesAndReasons

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.bavenir.ogwapi.commons.messages.CodesAndReasons

  • public class CodesAndReasons
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class with constants for status codes and status code reasons. Most of them are identical with standard HTTP codes and reasons (@see wiki article).
    Author:
    sulfo
